ays to their adaptation to modern-day Russia's free-wheeling oligarchy and global opportunities beyond.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 0aGangszRussia (Federation) 0aMafiazRussia (Federation) 0aOrganized crimezRussia (Federation) 0aPrison gangszRussia (Federation) 7aHISTORY / Russia & the Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300187625423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300187625.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles